 Programming, by Patrick Keuleers, Sr. Governance Adviser, UNDP RCB Risk Assessments in Governance and Capacity Development Programming, by Sandra Nicoll, Governance and Capacity Development, ADB Public Sector Reforms and Anti-Corruption Programming: Experience of Malaysia, by Mr. Anis Yusal Yusoff, Director, Political Sector, Institut Integriti Malaysia Rapporteur: Ms. Panvirush Vittayapraphakul, Programme Assistant, UNDP RCB 10.30\u201310.45 a.m. Coffee break Fifth session 10.45 a.m.\u201312.00 p.m. Anti-Corruption Programming for Public Sector Reform at National", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7c07eea3-b60d-4fd0-9ed4-bd752255dfe2": {"__data__": {"id_": "7c07eea3-b60d-4fd0-9ed4-bd752255dfe2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/supporting-uncac-implementation-country-experiences-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "Supporting UNCAC Implementation: Country Experiences in the Asia-Pacific Region", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/supporting-uncac-implementation-country-experiences-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations Development Programme", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "0a056da4e946ef654e622eb00383999751d1731279cda22365fe4430cbd78c14"}, "3": {"node_id": "7b4ed477-4f79-43a7-adf0-97168a436ae6", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.undp.org/asia-pacific/publications/supporting-uncac-implementation-country-experiences-asia-pacific-region", "Author": "United Nations Development Programme", "Publisher": "United Nations